name: Feather River Doors Rochester Fiberglass Double Door - Patina Caming
description: Feather River Doors Rochester 1/2 Lite is a Smooth Fiberglass Double Door with Patina Caming that is ready to paint. This door can be painted any color to match your homes decor. The Rochester Collection contemporary design with patina caming and clear bevel glass with shimmering cord glass surrounded by double granite, seedy, and pale gray glue chip glass. This door has all the long lasting benefits associated with fiberglass doors, a great look, along with a load of features and benefits usually viewed as upgrades with other doors plus Energy Efficient and Energy Star qualified. Door Spec: 72 in. x 80 in. Prehung Double Door with White Aluminum Astragal, 4-9/16 in.
